{"tid":279513,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[紐西蘭][曲折] Bain一家滅門案","createTime":"2017-06-11T10:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T15:12:29.000Z","uid":78785,"like":70,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4283efcb2f185149f38025cbf9caa2afa55034b","tid":279513,"uid":78785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">紐西蘭奇案：Bain一家滅門案</span> <br />\n</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/z9cp8s1g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz9cp8s1g&h=99b94754&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n我係一個中國論壇度搵到一篇寫得好好既文。今次我只係將所有大陸用字 e.g.譯音，動詞，轉番晒做我地呢邊既書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如果有錯請輕輕力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），同埋我係篇文入面加番一d我係新聞度搵到既證據而文中係無提到既。最後，我做左一個簡單既timeline同埋人物關係圖，以便無咁好心力既巴打了解件事。 所有Credit 歸果個論壇既作者，我只係補充同整合。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次呢單案，歷時十幾年，文有d長，但我覺得係值得睇既。之前幾個既posts，雖然有唔少証據，但其實並無太多佐證同比大家討論既餘地。今次呢單案件，控辯雙方就唔同既論點爭議左好耐，而每邊既理由都極之充分有理。<br />\n<br />\n呢單案，我覺得好有價值既地方，在於可以令大家反思司法制度既一d盲點。比如，即使可能個個都知係咁，但由於証據不足，所以不能落實；或者，佢明明好似真係無做過，但証據確鑿。講到底，証據係乜？ 証據，其實諗深一層，經過好多人既手，比如警方，再到法醫官，再到庭上。箇中過程，到底係咪完全公正？係咪無人做手腳？真係好難知。 就好似 Angelababy証明自己無整容一樣，搵左一個美容醫生去証明自己清白，但即使如此，好多人心底裡仍然唔信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到尾，到底係証據已經失去左公信力，定根本人類己經對所有事物失去信任？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢單案既精彩，就在於此。希望巴絲打們唔會因爲佢長文所以唔睇到尾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">話說..........</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頂要去同屋企人食飯，今晚再出文，sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddfcf8ed9cb0713119abbd6078ff0510ad14aa5","tid":279513,"uid":41552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"釣人癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00ab534bbe3d28406a14e05324899e9cc734dfc","tid":279513,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"枉我仲睇晒咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de1862678470b0e65836fb275a02dd129ffced9","tid":279513,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"等我仲以為有文睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eed38a23aa71dc457252f493a681e102d464275","tid":279513,"uid":78785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等我仲以為有文睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我出左個頭之後話要食飯，好快，一個鐘。"},{"pid":"a4da5bd2c78fae0d20763c7ae83b0508236b6a04","tid":279513,"uid":8346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0d28ca98718b3cba2ef8bedd4a601d428a59fe","tid":279513,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> G持"},{"pid":"1dc546b3f9eba001604c147288c5f50621b08690","tid":279513,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e0c446036a30321b1cc0adfaf242cd81142369","tid":279513,"uid":118661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T1